    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a mechanically sorted example of the S54-powered icon. The 3.2L inline-six delivers linear power through its individual throttle bodies, bolstered by a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and a recently refreshed cooling system. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and the factory M-variable limited-slip differential. Critical chassis maintenance has been addressed, including subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity during high-lateral-G cornering. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with a well-maintained driver, the suspension geometry remains tight and the steering rack communicative. A turn-key performance machine for the discerning driver.",
      "price": 34500.0,
