      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been absolutely wonderful to me. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014super reliable and perfect for someone looking for a dependable daily driver without the 'brand new' price tag. I've taken great care of it, and it runs like a dream! If you're looking for a comfortable, well-loved car that still has tons of life left in it, you've found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions; I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
